row.InputSentence1: Joey worked for a great company but her hours were cut.
row.InputSentence2: The company said they had to let her go and laid her off.
row.InputSentence3: Joey began looking for another job right away.
row.InputSentence4: She had a hard time finding work but gave job searching her all.
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz1: Joey finally received a call from an employer and got the job.
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz2: Joey spent her days playing video games.
